&lt;li class=&quot;font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2&quot;&gt;Design analytics visualizations, dashboards, and reports in OAC that translate business requirements into actionable metrics and storytelling.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2&quot;&gt;Establish data architecture standards, documentation practices, and reusable analytics patterns; mentor junior team members.&lt;/li&gt;
